---
// About section V4 - Colorful Bento
import certData from '../data/certificados.json';
const certCount = certData.certificados.length;
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mb-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
        Sobre la <span class="text-brand-purple">Visión</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Construir software es como armar un rompecabezas donde cada pieza debe encajar perfectamente: desde la capa de datos hasta la interfaz del usuario. Mi enfoque es transformar problemas complejos en <strong class="text-white">soluciones eficientes y seguras.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bento Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 auto-rows-[250px]">
    
    <!-- Big Architect Card -->
    <div class="bento-card bento-card-hover md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col justify-end relative shadow-2xl" style="--hover-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3)">
      <!-- Background pattern/color block -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-bl from-brand-purple/20 via-brand-blue/10 to-transparent blur-[80px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-purple shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)] flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-auto relative z-10">
         <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Orquestación de Ecosistemas</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          No creo en escribir código aislado. He diseñado arquitecturas completas: desde un backend robusto en Java y Spring Boot, pasando por apps móviles offline-first en Flutter, hasta utilidades perimetrales en Python.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Small Stats Card 1 -->
    <div class="bento-card bento-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative" style="--hover-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2)">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-emerald/5 blur-[40px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <span class="text-6xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-emerald to-emerald-800 mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">
        +{certCount}
      </span>
      <span class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-widest">
        Certificaciones
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Small Stats Card 2 -->
    <div class="bento-card bento-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center relative" style="--hover-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2)">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-brand-cyan/20 blur-[40px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="mb-4 text-brand-cyan">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 inline-block filter drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Ciberseguridad Práctica</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400">Scapy / Sniffing / Python</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
